ography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/psychosis-schizophrenia/references/\">American Psychiatric Association, 2013</a>], and the BMJ Best Practice guideline <em>Schizophrenia</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/psychosis-schizophrenia/references/\">BMJ Best Practice, 2019</a>].</p><!-- end field f4efde8e-488f-4fcc-ba5b-539533847d8a --><!-- end item 425a7f14-647d-4651-835d-26854af03b49 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}